headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Free Drinks and Vehicles Discounts
content:
Feel free to let loose and get carried away with free drinks at open bars at Nightclubs across the city and in The Diamond Casino & Resort. Plus, there are an array of vehicles on sale, including

- Übermacht SC1- 30% off
- Enus Stafford - 40% off
- Benefactor Turreted Limo – 40% off
- Vapid Flash GT – 40% off

And More! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
